          <p class="has-text-align-left has-brand-green-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-f899f9e8d261b8cfc1dc2420557f7024" id="homepage-multi-site-management-subtext" style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.44">Manage multiple WordPress sites from one place, get volume discounts on hosting products, and earn up to 50% revenue share when you migrate sites to our platform and refer our products to clients.</p> 
          <div style="height:0px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer wp-container-content-10"></div> 
