               <section class="c-menu-item mzp-has-icon"> <a class="c-menu-item-link" href="https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/?utm_source=www.mozilla.org&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=nav&amp;utm_content=innovation" data-link-text="Common Voice" data-link-type="nav" data-link-position="topnav" data-link-group="innovation"> <img loading="lazy" class="c-menu-item-icon" src="https://www.mozilla.org/media/img/nav/icons/icon-common-voice.127fa3f5dcb0.svg" alt=""> <h4 class="c-menu-item-title">Common Voice</h4> <p class="c-menu-item-desc">Donate your voice so the future of the web can hear everyone.</p> </a> 
               </section> </li> 
