       <div class="mzp-c-picto-body"> <a href="https://fakespot.com/?utm_source=www.mozilla.org&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=homepage" class="mzp-c-button mzp-t-secondary" id="homepage-get-fakespot" data-cta-text="Get Fakespot" data-cta-type="link">Get Fakespot</a> 
